        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "ViMka",
          "name": "h2sub",
          "fill": "#64748B",
          "content": "Isolation données, canaux dédiés, RBAC indépendant, config LLM séparée, billing par instance",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "yB8Jp",
          "name": "row2",
          "width": 1920,
          "height": "fill_container",
          "gap": 16,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "1bnl5",
              "name": "whyBox",
              "width": 320,
              "height": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#EEF2FF",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#6366F1"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "qGNdV",
                  "name": "whyT",
                  "fill": "#4338CA",
                  "content": "Pourquoi 1 instance / client",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "5YgSE",
                  "name": "why1",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "content": "• [channels.whatsapp] = table unique\n  → 1 seul bot/numéro par canal\n\n• Isolation SQLite complète\n  → zéro risque de fuite de données\n\n• RBAC indépendant\n  → client = owner de son instance\n\n• Config LLM séparée\n  → Claude, GPT-4, Groq par client\n\n• Billing simple\n  → GET /api/usage/summary par instance\n\n• Blast radius limité\n  → si instance A crash, B pas impacté",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "edyaV",
              "name": "costBox",
              "width": 320,
              "height": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#F0FDF4",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#22C55E"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "xgN5K",
                  "name": "costT",
                  "fill": "#166534",
                  "content": "Coûts estimés",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Ai6nj",
                  "name": "costD",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "content": "1 instance OpenFang :\n  ~40MB RAM idle\n  ~32MB disque\n\nHetzner CX22 (4GB, 4.35€/mois) :\n  → ~80 clients idle\n  → ~30-40 clients actifs\n\nHetzner CX32 (8GB, 7.49€/mois) :\n  → ~160 clients idle\n  → ~60-80 clients actifs\n\nAzure Container Apps :\n  → Scale-to-zero\n  → ~0.50-2€/client/mois\n\nMarge brute :\n  80-95% sur Hetzner\n  60-80% sur Azure",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "NE7m7",
              "name": "provBox",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFF7ED",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#F97316"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 12,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "WjGvs",
                  "name": "provT",
                  "fill": "#C2410C",
                  "content": "Flux de provisioning",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "LUcj1",
                  "name": "provD",
                  "fill": "#334155",
                  "content": "1. Client souscrit → Stripe webhook\n\n2. Go crée tenant en PostgreSQL\n\n3. Go génère config.toml :\n   • api_listen, api_key\n   • mode: stable\n   • [default_model] provider\n   • [[users]] name, role: owner\n   • [network] shared_secret\n\n4. Go lance container Docker :\n   docker run -d \\\n     --name openfang-{tenant_id} \\\n     --memory=512m --cpus=1 \\\n     -p {api_port}:50051\n\n5. Health check OK :\n   GET /api/health\n\n6. Crée agent par défaut :\n   POST /api/agents\n\n7. Configure canaux → restart\n\n8. Email bienvenue → client",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 9,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
